description: Performs 25 mc runs around each integer point in 0.05 half-width interval around predicted PT with james stein denoiser. Sparsity varies in fraction from 0.05 to 0.95 in increments of 0.05. No. of rows varies in [100, 200, 400, 600, 800, 1000] and no. of columns is 5. Jacobian approximated by randomly selecting about min(150, signal_nrow) rows of the estimated signal.
